  • Fields 
    Field Description
    im.zego.zegoexpress.entity.ZegoEngineConfig.logConfig

  • Methods 
    Method Description
    im.zego.zegoexpress.callback.IZegoEventHandler.onPlayerRecvSEI​(String, byte[])
    This function will switch the UI thread callback data, which may cause SEI data exceptions. It will be deprecated in version 3.4.0 and above. Please use the [onPlayerSyncRecvSEI] function instead.
    im.zego.zegoexpress.ZegoCopyrightedMusic.getLrcLyric​(String, IZegoCopyrightedMusicGetLrcLyricCallback)
    Deprecated since 2.14.0, please use the method with the same name with [vendorID] parameter instead.

    Deprecated since 3.0.2, please use the [getSharedResource] function instead.

    Deprecated since 2.14.0, please use the method with the same name with [vendorID] parameter instead.
    im.zego.zegoexpress.ZegoCopyrightedMusic.requestAccompaniment​(ZegoCopyrightedMusicRequestConfig, IZegoCopyrightedMusicRequestAccompanimentCallback)
    Deprecated since 3.0.2, please use the [requestResource] function instead.

    Deprecated since 3.0.2, please use the [requestResource] function instead.
    im.zego.zegoexpress.ZegoExpressEngine.createEngine​(long, String, boolean, ZegoScenario, Application, IZegoEventHandler)
    Deprecated since 2.14.0, please use the method with the same name without [isTestEnv] parameter instead.
    im.zego.zegoexpress.ZegoExpressEngine.enableBeautify​(int)
    Deprecated since 2.16.0, please use the [enableEffectsBeauty] function instead.
    im.zego.zegoexpress.ZegoExpressEngine.setBeautifyOption​(ZegoBeautifyOption)
    Deprecated since 2.16.0, please use the [setEffectsBeautyParam] function instead.
